descriptor.name: Chip Chops Dog Treat Diced Chicken, 70 g
descriptor.long_desc:
Chip Chops Diced Chicken are made of fresh chicken. They are carefully prepared to provide a pure, tasty and highly digestible snack. Chip Chops dog treats has goodness with nutritional benefits for your pet’s well being. These will definitely be the favorite snacks in no time. Chip Chops dog treats are suitable for feeding as a snack or a reward to show your pet love.

- Delightfully crunchy every day treats for your pet
- Contains high amount of proteins that helps in building and repairing muscles, and other body tissues
- Carefully prepared to provide a pure, tasty and highly digestible snack
- Free of sugar

About the Brand: Chip Chops is a great way to keep your pooch motivated and encouraged to learn. While training your dog, it is a must to keep rewarding the dog to reinforce good behaviour. It is one such snack; as it is made of fresh meat. This dog snack provides a pure, tasty and highly digestible treat. This treat is filled with nutritional goodness and is suitable for feeding as a snack, rewards for good behaviour and to show your pet love with some indulgent pampering.

descriptor.name: Shan Chicken Masala, 50 g
descriptor.long_desc:
Shan Chicken Masala Mix helps you to prepare a rich and aromatic chicken curry for an appetizing and flavourful treat. Simply follow the recipe provided on the back of the box for a delicious meal that your whole family will enjoy garnish with finely chopped green chilies, ginger, and lime juice.

- Seasoning mix for chicken in yoghurt curry
- Made using the finest quality ingredients and authentic spices
- No artificial colors or preservatives

About the Brand: Shan Foods Limited is a global producer of packaged spice mixes, primarily used in South Asian dishes. The company was established in 1981 as a single-room operation by its founder, Sikander Sultan, in Pakistan and quickly grew from there to becoming a major player in the packaged spice mixes industry.

descriptor.name: Boheco Himalayan Hemp Hearts, 100 g
descriptor.short_desc:
- Munch, garnish or mix with any kind of snacks, meals, batters, or smoothies

Country of Origin: India
descriptor.long_desc:
Nutrition-packed goodness of nature, Boheco Hemp Hearts are sorted and shelled with care to bring out the nutty flavor that compliments all your dishes. Hemp hearts are one of the best plant-based sources of protein and omegas that are essential for your everyday nutritional needs.

- A quick fix source of nutrition that is essential for your everyday nutritional needs
- Provide a beneficial balance of fatty acids, Omega-6 and Omega-3, Vitamin A, and Vitamin C
- Helps boost energy levels, enhances muscle function, promotes weight loss, and strengthens immunity
- NON-GMO, no additives, and GMP certified

About the Brand: Bombay Hemp Company a.k.a. BOHECO, incorporated in 2013, is an agro-based enterprise reimagining the future of Indian agriculture and healthy living with Hemp and Cannabis as their lens. The uses of cannabis are kaleidoscopic. Pull out its fiber, and it will give you yarn; harvest its seeds for wholesome nutrition; study its genetics, and you’ll find medicine; chop it into softwood for material to build a shelter. Their design fuses this potential with the existing industries of agriculture, technology, nutrition, and healthcare; to bring together community, impact, and value.

descriptor.name: Boheco Himalayan Hemp Hearts, 100 g
descriptor.short_desc:
- Munch, garnish or mix with any kind of snacks, meals, batters, or smoothies

Country of Origin: India
descriptor.long_desc:
Nutrition-packed goodness of nature, Boheco Hemp Hearts are sorted and shelled with care to bring out the nutty flavor that compliments all your dishes. Hemp hearts are one of the best plant-based sources of protein and omegas that are essential for your everyday nutritional needs.

- A quick fix source of nutrition that is essential for your everyday nutritional needs
- Provide a beneficial balance of fatty acids, Omega-6 and Omega-3, Vitamin A, and Vitamin C
- Helps boost energy levels, enhances muscle function, promotes weight loss, and strengthens immunity
- NON-GMO, no additives, and GMP certified

About the Brand: Bombay Hemp Company a.k.a. BOHECO, incorporated in 2013, is an agro-based enterprise reimagining the future of Indian agriculture and healthy living with Hemp and Cannabis as their lens. The uses of cannabis are kaleidoscopic. Pull out its fiber, and it will give you yarn; harvest its seeds for wholesome nutrition; study its genetics, and you’ll find medicine; chop it into softwood for material to build a shelter. Their design fuses this potential with the existing industries of agriculture, technology, nutrition, and healthcare; to bring together community, impact, and value.
